data.description: Charming three-bedroom three-bath home. Relax and unwind on the cozy front porch. As you step inside notice the cozy living room and beautiful wood floors. The kitchen has beautiful dark wood cabinets and granite countertops. This is a special home! It could use a fresh coat of paint to make it your own. Roof and HVAC are 6 years old. House could use a little TLC, jacuzzi tub in master bedroom needs a new pump. Seller is willing to negotiate appraisal repairs depending on offer but currently priced based on needing work.
